						Its really amazing what Verant does.  If this is the "official" strategy guide, its makes one wonder what Verant cares about, the truth about the game or making it sound more complex and appealing to people that don't have it yet.  IMHO, I believe they should of at least asked some game guides if not some players to help with the making of this guide.  Personally, it disappoints me to see a butchered description of EverQuest to be allowed for everyone to see.
						
						</font>
